{"tid":2451717,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大職員串謀詐騙 1被告已認罪將以控方證人出庭","createTime":"2021-03-18T09:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T12:08:23.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eea2a8ad199739be158e4fd0e5857be6998008ec","tid":2451717,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"中大伍宜孫書院及善衡書院3名職員，疑在小型工程投標過程中，隱瞞與一名裝修公司東主的關係，並使用其他公司的虛假報價單，令投標過程合符中大規定的競爭性，東主終在價低者得原則下，承辦了總值逾220萬元的小型工程訂單。4人被控偽造、公職人員行為失當、串謀詐騙等罪，案件今在區域法院開審。<br />\n<br />\n被告為中大伍宜孫書院的院務主任李珮珊（43歲）、李珮珊妹夫暨新生活創意設計東主彭兆衡（38歲）、中大伍宜孫書院行政主任石曉風（40歲）、善衡書院二級計劃協調員梁祐誠（36歲）；梁祐誠早前已承認串謀詐騙罪，將以控方證人身份出庭作供。<br />\n<br />\n控方開案陳詞指，中大《大學採購及招標程序》規定，大學在批出小型工程撥款前，須先索取至少2份報價單，並採用價低者得採購原則。若職員在過程中涉及任何利益衝突，必須呈交書面聲明。"},{"pid":"72a934d1fe4cfc0494c41d0935024d81c9e3f59c","tid":2451717,"uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:58:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/2025426/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2025426%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2QFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=6cae2941\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2025426%2F&h=fdf497b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/2025426/</a>"},{"pid":"26f4d1897145d54d8fae3a4142dda743f55e3c6e","tid":2451717,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"出賣手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d9ecd393a599309e19d78193b56e27be671ee1","tid":2451717,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26f4d1897145d54d8fae3a4142dda743f55e3c6e","tid":2451717,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"出賣手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:00:1